text: Jeanne or Joan of France may refer to: * Jeanne III, Countess of Burgundy (1308–1349) * Joan II of Navarre (1312–1349) * Jeanne de Valois, Queen of Navarre (1343–1373) * Joan of Valois (1351–1371) * Joan of France (1391–1433) * Joan of France, Duchess of Bourbon (1435–1482) * Joan of France, Duchess of Berry (1464–1505)
title: Joan of France
